<hr/>
<form action="" method="post" name="bug_report" style="font-size: 12px;"  onsubmit="validate_bug_details();">
<label> Enter steps to reproduce issue/crash : </label>
<br/>
<textarea rows="5" cols="50" name="issue_details">
</textarea>
<br/>
<input type="checkbox" name="h_device_model" value=""><div id="fld1" style="display:inline;">Device model</div>
<br/>
<input type="checkbox" name="h_firmware_version" value=""><div id="fld2" style="display:inline;">Device model</div>
<br/>
<input type="checkbox" name="h_symbian_version" value=""><div id="fld3" style="display:inline;">Device model</div>
<br/>
<input type="checkbox" name="h_s60_version" value=""><div id="fld4" style="display:inline;">Device model</div>
<br/>
<input type="checkbox" name="h_imei_hash" value=""><div id="fld8" style="display:inline;word-wrap: break-word;">Device model</div>
<br/>
<br/>
<label>Enter email-id : </label> <input size="50" type="text" name="presence_email" maxlength="256" />
<br/>
<br/>
<div style="text-align:center;">
<button type="submit">Report Bug</button>
</form>
<hr/>
<div id="presence" style="display: block;font-size: 12px;">
If entering the details using mobile is cumbersome, then visit http://brahma.flaminghorns.com/bugs.html to report the issue/crash.
</div> 
